high_descs: Walk forward to the stove top.
Pick up the tomato on the counter to the left of the kettle.
Turn left and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the tomato in the refrigerator for a few seconds, then take it out and close the refrigerator.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink basin, to the left of the other tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled tomato in a sink.
